snippet.title: Fracctal Monster Trailer (P2E Monster Taming Game)
snippet.description: Fracctal Monsters is a play-and-earn virtual petcare game built on the Algorand blockchain. It uses Algorand NFTs to simulate the growth and evolution of unique pets and is a progression of classic Web2 games such as Neopets, Tamagotchi, and Webkinz. If you are a fan of quality virtual pet games, then Fracctal Monsters is a must-try!
